title: Cafe Greg
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Middle Eastern, Kosher, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves fish, veg options available. Branch of Cafe Greg chain inside a big shopping mall in the Ra'anana Industrial Zone. There is a separate vegan menu with salads like the summer salad and legume salad, a few Asian-influenced dishes like stir-fries and curry, a big breakfast, plus shakshouka made with antipasti vegetables.
streetAddress: Renanim Shopping Mall, Ra'anana Industrial Zone, HaTa'asiya St
